<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Due to <a href="http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc1939#page-11">http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc1939#page-11</a> the TOP-command needs two arguments. The Zend implementation was used to provide just the first argument, when the second was &lt; 1 or false. Eg. Gmail could not be used with that implementation. Fixed in the following patch.</p>

